<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Láskavé puto | Michaela</title>
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@500&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-bg: #fdfaf8;
            --text-main: #4a4a4a;
            --text-sub: #8c7b75;
            --accent-color: #e0d5d0;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --hover-bg: #fcf6f4;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--primary-bg);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 2px solid var(--white);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        
        .profile-img span {
            font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--text-sub);
        }

        .main-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--text-sub);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px; 
        }

        .btn {
            display: block;
            padding: 16px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: var(--white);
            color: var(--text-main);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--hover-bg);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            border-color: #d1c1ba;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
        }

        .btn-featured {
            background-color: #f7f1ee; 
            border-color: #d8c8c2;
        }

        .footer-quote {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-sub);
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-style: italic;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        
        <div class="profile-img">
            <span>M</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="main-title">Láskavé puto</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Kde sa láskavosť k sebe mení na pokojný domov.</p>

        <div class="button-container">
           
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-featured">
                📖 Pridaj sa na waitlist: Sprievodca 'Mami, som doma.'
            </a>

            <a href="https://preview.mailerlite.io/preview/2095142/sites/183670813147268831/laskave-puto-waitlist"_blank">
                🌿 ZADARMO 7 viet, ktoré upokoja tvoje dieťa
            </a>
            
            <a href="https://subscribepage.io/7-day-solo-date-challenge" class="btn" target="_blank">
                ✨ ZADARMO 30 sekúnd, ktoré zmenia vaše poobedie
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-quote">
            "Emócia, ktorá dostane priestor vyjadriť sa v tvojom objatí, sa nemusí premeniť na hnev."
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
